984
01:27:08,833 --> 01:27:09,708
Obrigada.

985
01:27:34,750 --> 01:27:40,583
A SAM BLOOM PASSOU A COMPETIR
NOS CAMPEONATOS MUNDIAIS DE CAIAQUE

986
01:27:40,666 --> 01:27:46,541
